# warnings

## INEFFECTIVE_DYNAMIC_IMPORT

```text
[INEFFECTIVE_DYNAMIC_IMPORT] file.json is dynamically imported by main.js but also statically imported by main.js, dynamic import will not move module into another chunk.

```

